{"text":"Hi Michael, are you referring to the bolt and spring nut I installed at "},{"text":"15:00","videoLink":{"externalVideoId":"of8Gc_mE3ic","startTimeSeconds":900}},{"text":"? Basically there are only two bolts holding the crossbar to the main rails.  This has been super stable for the past year.  I hope this helps."}

{"text":"Great question, I had the same thought but it turns out that Washington State Ferries got rid of the over height surcharge for vehicles under 22'.
